title: Senior Bowl Quarterback Interviews

description:
DJ & Bucky recap day 1 of Senior Bowl practice in Mobile (0:30). Then, the guys interview Missouri QB Drew Lock (5:30), Auburn QB Jarrett Stidham (16:50) & NC State QB Ryan Finley (28:40).
